I think the syntax is something like
```{% macro your_macro() %}
  &lt;div class="whatever"&gt;
    {{ caller() }}
  &lt;/div&gt;
{% endmacro %}

{% call your_macro() %}
  This will appear where "caller()" is.
{% endcall %}```
